snippet.title: Alien Shooter (Java Mobile) - 5 Minutes Gameplay
snippet.description:
Alien Shooter is a mobile java game for old cellphones. You are a agent and needs do your job: clear the world of the aliens. And for this, you are  loaded of heavy weapons and explosives.

Eliminate the aliens and recovery the world peace.
